<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4449.1.1>
    dc:creator "Chani-Posse, Mariana", "Hansen, Aslak Kappel", "Newton, Alfred F.", "Solodovnikov, Alexey" ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "Checklist and taxonomic changes for Central and South American Philonthina (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae)" ;
    bibo:endPage "95" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2018-07-20" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "4449" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454307>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454309>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454315> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454307>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–12 [BMNH ©]. Type material (habitus and labels): 1, 2, Philonthus abnormalis Sharp, lectotype; 3, 4, Philonthus celatus Sharp, lectotype; 5, 6, Philonthus corticalis Sharp, holotype; 7, 8, Philonthus extremus Sharp, holotype; 9, 10, Philonthus latecinctus Sharp, lectotype; 11, 12, Philonthus muticus Sharp, lectotype. Scale bar= 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454307/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454309>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–24 [BMNH ©]. Type material (habitus and labels): 13, 14, Philonthus optatus Sharp, holotype; 15, 16, Philonthus platypterus Sharp, lectotype; 17, 18, Philonthus rufiventris Sharp, holotype; 19, 20, Philonthus rufocaudus Sharp, lectotype; 21, 22, Philonthus rufopygus Sharp, lectotype; 23, 24, Philonthus serraticornis Sharp, holotype. Scale bar= 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454309/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454315>
    dc:description "FIGURES 45–52 [FMNH ©]. Type and non-type material (habitus and labels): 45, 46, Belonuchus penetrans Silvestri, nontype; 47, 48, Philonthus excelsus Bernhauer, syntype; 49, 50 Philonthus peruvianus Bernhauer, syntype; 51, 52, Philonthus subaeneipennis Bernhauer, holotype. Scale bar= 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454315/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

